<div class="header-text">
  <ul>
    <li><h2>My Treasure Chest</h2></li>
    <li><h4>...Come inside!</h4></li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="span9">
    <div class="container-treasure">
      <div class="sign-up">
        <h3>Sign Up</h3>
          <h4>Thanks for coming with me on this one!</h4>
          <p>If you sign up below, I might drop you a line occassionally to keep you posted on tour dates, releases and other Herbert news. I promise I won't share your details or clog your mailbox with junk (promise).</p>
          <p>To keep you coming back to see me, from time to time I will update the Treasure Chest with exclusive tracks, demos, photos, promo codes and all manner of Gwyn related paraphanalia! You can also leave me a message on the notice board and I'll do my best to reply to as many of you as possible.</p>
          <p>All you have to do is complete the form below, and check your inbox for an email with a link to confirm your address. Click on the link and you will be directed back to this page to claim your free track.</p>
          <p>Happy downloading!</p>
          <p>Gwyn</p>
          <%= form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
          <h4><%= f.email_field :email, :autofocus => true, :placeholder => "Enter your email here - hit return to submit" %><%= f.submit "Sign in" %></h4>
          <% end %>
          <h4><%= link_to "Sign In", new_session_path(resource_name) %></h4>
          <h4><%= link_to "Didn't Receive Confirmation Instructions?", new_confirmation_path(resource_name) %></h4>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="span3">
    <%= render 'layouts/menu' %>
  </div>
</div>